<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.3.10">
<l>tuyakkaṟu matiyiṉaṉ ñāṉattu ḷamararait tuyakku</l>
<l>mayakkuṭai māyaikaḷ vāṉilum periyaṉa vallaṉ</l>
<l>puyalkaru niṟattaṉaṉ perunilaṅ kaṭanta nallaṭippō</l>
<l>tayarppila ṉalaṟṟuvaṉ ṟaḻuvuvaṉ vaṇaṅkuva ṉamarntē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who masters the things that are great in heaven, confusing illusions</l>
<l>that hold the immortals spellbound with knowledgable hearts, with bond-free minds,</l>
<l>he with the dark colour of rain clouds, I cannot forget the buds [which are his] good feet</l>
<l>that traversed the vast ground, I shall talk on, I shall embrace, I shall constantly bow.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
